		"description": {
			"public": "<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); font-family: var(--nimble-primary-font); margin-block: 0px\"><strong>Rarity</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: &#x27;Roboto Condensed&#x27;, sans-serif\"><strong>:</strong> Legendary</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); font-family: var(--nimble-primary-font); margin-block: 0px\"><strong>Spell level</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: &#x27;Roboto Condensed&#x27;, sans-serif\"><strong>:</strong> Tier 9</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); font-family: var(--nimble-primary-font); margin-block: 0px\"><strong>Charges</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: &#x27;Roboto Condensed&#x27;, sans-serif\"><strong>:</strong> 1</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); font-family: var(--nimble-primary-font); margin-block: 0px\"><strong>Recharge</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: &#x27;Roboto Condensed&#x27;, sans-serif\"><strong>:</strong> Give an ancient dragon a gift it truly desires.</span></p><hr><p><strong>Actions:</strong> 5</p><p>Transform into a Huge dragon. Gain 3 actions, a fly speed of 12, LVL Armor, 10×LVL temp HP, and:</p><ul><li><p>Tooth & Claw. Action: (Reach 2) [[/r 1d20+@level]]{1d20+LVL} damage (ignoring armor). Inflicts smoldering.</p></li><li><p>Immolating Breath. 2 Actions: (Reach: Cone 8). DC 20 DEX save, [[/r (@key)d20]]{KEY d20} damage, half on save. Smoldering targets fail.</p></li></ul><p>You can maintain this form for as long as the temp HP granted by this spell remain (max. 10 minutes). When it ends, you drop to 0 HP.</p>",
